<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5029392>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Senotainia (Arrenopus) albifrons (Rd.). ♂, Israel: Ein Avdat N[ational] P[arc], Nahal Zin, 17. v.2006 (K. Szpila): (a) ‒ total view laterally; (b) ‒ head anteriorly; (c) ‒ head dorsally; (d) ‒ fore left tarsus dorsally; (e) ‒ abdomen dorsally. Figure 2. Senotainia (s. str.) caspica Rohd. ♂, Israel: Hallia, 25.iii.1975 (K. Szpila): (a) ‒ head anteriorly; (b) ‒ head laterally; (c) ‒ head dorsally; (d) ‒ abdomen dorsally; ♀, Israel: Ein Mur, 31. iii.1981: (e) ‒ total view laterally; (f) ‒ head laterally; (g) ‒ head dorsally; (h) ‒ wing; (i) ‒ abdomen dorsally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5029392/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5029396>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Senotainia (s. str.) flava Verves & Khrokalo, n. sp. ♀, Israel: Holotype: (a) ‒ total view laterally; (b) ‒ total view dorsally; (c) ‒ head anteriorly; (d) ‒ head laterally; (e) ‒ head dorsally; (f) ‒ abdomen dorsally. Figure 6. Senotainia (s. str.) paradeserta Verves & Khrokalo, n. sp. ♂, Holotype:(a) ‒ total view laterally; (b) ‒ total view dorsally; (c) ‒ head anteriorly; (d) ‒ head laterally; (e) ‒ head dorsally; (f) ‒ wing; (g) ‒ postabdomen; ♀, Paratype: (h) ‒ head anteriorly; ‒ (i) head laterally; (k) ‒ wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5029396/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5029394>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Senotainia (s. str.) conica (Fll.). ♂, Poland: Torun-lotnisko, 26.vii.2001 (K. Szpila): (a) ‒ total view laterally; (b) ‒ head anteriorly; (c) ‒ head laterally; (d) ‒ abdomen dorsally. Figure 4. Senotainia (s. str.) deserta Rohd. ♂, Israel: Ma’agan Mikha’el Beach, 7 m, 32°34.6ʹ N/34°54.9ʹ E, 30.vi.2010 (K. Szpila): (a) ‒ total view laterally; (b) ‒ head anteriorly; (c) ‒ head laterally; (d) ‒ head dorsally; (e) ‒ wing; (f) ‒ abdomen dorsally; ♀, Israel: Ma’agan Mikha’el, 21.ix.2010: (g) ‒ total view laterally; (h) ‒ head anteriorly; (i) ‒ head laterally; (k) ‒ head dorsally; (l) ‒ wing; (m) ‒ abdomen dorsally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5029394/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5029398>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Senotainia (s. str.) similis Verves & Khrokalo, n. sp. ♂, Holotype: (a) ‒ total view laterally; (b) ‒ total view dorsally; (c) ‒ head anteriorly; (d) ‒ head laterally; (e) ‒ head dorsally; (f) – abdomen posteriorly. Figure 8. Senotainia (s. str.) tricuspis (Mg.). ♂, Spain: Valencia, Pinet, dunes, 23.v.2011 (K. Szpila): (a) ‒ total view laterally; (b) ‒ total view dorsally; (c) ‒ head anteriorly; (d) ‒ head laterally; (e) – head dorsally; (f) ‒ wing; (g) ‒ abdomen dorsally; ♀, Spain:Valencia,Pinet, dunes, 23.v.2011: (h) ‒ total view laterally; (i) ‒ total view dorsally; (k) ‒ head anteriorly; (l) ‒ head dorsally; (m) ‒ head laterally; (n) ‒ wing; (o) ‒ abdomen dorsally." ;
